latestIgtvVideos.title: DAY 1
latestIgtvVideos.caption:
What a way to kickstart the second edition of @namascrayexperience ! 
Amidst the electric energy and enigmatic sets, it was a night to remember. 

With best indigenous talents like  @corridorsmusic , @sakrel_ , @ayeshapramanik , @sixthocean warming up the dance floor, @mathame_ illuminating the stage with their melodic tunes, @kohra_  and @b_u_l_l_z_e_y_e welcomed the sunrise with their deep moving tracks,
all adding an unforgettable start to the event.

Rousing the crowd to diverse rhythms, this stellar lineup kept everyone bouncing to the beats at DAY 1 of @namascrayexperience 

📽️ - @fleckmedia
